HEADWORD: Equilibrist
<hw>E*quil"i*brist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
balances himself in unnatural positions and hazardous movements; a
balancer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When the <qex>equilibrist</qex> balances a rod upon his
finger.</q> <rj><qau>Stewart.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Equilibrity</ent>⟦br⟧
